  <summary date="2021-05-24T20:13:43Z" status="Introduced in House">COVID-19 Eviction Consumer Report Fairness Act

 This bill prohibits from inclusion in a consumer credit report information related to an eviction occurring during the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) national emergency or occurring in the 120 days after the termination of such emergency.</summary>
